// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0437 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 7b94acc4-5f4f-5296-8640-910f5866959c

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
